{
  "stem": "3475.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were those wagons, you know, railroad cars that kind of tilted sideways to dump-- to dump out the dirt and tilted upright to load them up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had to work all day in the hot sun with very little food, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when you work hard, you need more food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So a lot of people were just dying there, you know, getting too weak.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when you got too weak, they sent you to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I felt the life ebbing out of me, you know, that I would not survive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After about three days or four days, I said, I'm not going to make it anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took courage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the, the, the Lageralteste, who was the head of the whole-- of the whole camp, of Buna Werke, was a big German.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a green triangle, which indicated that he was a [GERMAN], which means a criminal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he, he was the head of the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was big, about 6 feet 4 or something, like, big, giant man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so on Sunday, when we didn't work, I took courage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went, and I walked up to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stood upright and saluted him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told him in German that I would like to have a few words to tell him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he let me say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him the whole story, you know, what happened, that I am, by training, a, you know, a Maschine Schlosser and that I'm dying there in this.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what purpose do I serve?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, at least, if I work at my profession, I will serve some purpose for Germany, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took down my number, you know, which is 127915.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wrote it down.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
